Summary: nothing like i have ever seen before, shocked!
divs: Sighting DetailsI was walking my dog here in Seminole, Florida on December 12, 2011 and I was distracted by a HUGE TRIANGLE SHIP above me with FOUR HUGE LIGHTS on its underbelly. I stared at this object for a moment, then reached into my pocket and pulled out my i-phone and snapped off a few pictures of it as it made its way off int the distance. I was able to get these two shots. When I blew these up on my i-phone you can clearly see a TRIANGLE ship with FOUR HUGE LIGHTS.
